    bibo:volume "4150" ;
    dc:creator "Reid, C. A. M.; Beatson, M." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the stag beetle genus Ryssonotus MacLeay (Coleoptera: Lucanidae), with descriptions of a new genus and three new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272085>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272087>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272090>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272089>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272091>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272094>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272096>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272097> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272085>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 − 9. Habitus, male: 1, Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 2, Safrina dekeyzeri new species; 3, S. grandis (Lea, 1915); 4, S. jaedoni new species; 5, S. jugularis (Westwood, 1863); 6, S. laticeps (MacLeay, 1885); 7, S. moorei new species; 8, S. parallela (Deyrolle, 1881); 9, S. polita (Carter, 1921)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272087>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 − 27. Head, dorsal, male: 19, Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 20, Safrina dekeyzeri new species; 21, S. grandis (Lea, 1915); 22, S. jaedoni new species; 23, S. laticeps (MacLeay, 1885); 24, S. jugularis (Westwood, 1863); 25, S. moorei new species; 26, S. parallela (Deyrolle, 1881); 27, S. polita (Carter, 1921)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272090>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 − 43. Lateral views of male head, Safrina species: 39, S. dekeyzeri new species; 40, S. grandis (Lea, 1915); 41, S. jaedoni new species; 42, S. moorei new species; 43, S. polita (Carter, 1921)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272090/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272089>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 − 38. Male antennal club: 37, Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 38, Safrina dekeyzeri new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272091>
    dc:description "FIGURES 44 − 45. Ventral part of head and prothorax: 44, male Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 45, female Safrina polita (Carter, 1921)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272094>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 − 51. Male genitalia, paraprocts, proctiger (left) and sternite IX (right): 50, Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 51, Safrina laticeps (MacLeay, 1885)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272094/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272096>
    dc:description "FIGURES 61 − 62. Female genitalia, dorsal (D), ventral (V), lateral (L) and softparts (S): 61, Ryssonotus nebulosus (Kirby, 1819); 62, Safrina jaedoni new species. Shading indicates density of sclerotisation, setae omitted except half of ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272096/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272097>
    dc:description "FIGURES 63 − 67. Larval morphology, Safrina laticeps (Macleay, 1885): 63, antenna; 64, left mandible; 65, mesocoxa; 66, metathoracic leg; 67, apex of venter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

